ERP System of the Blue Marble system will be the master system for the material code or the item

Price system, discount and all the other stuff will be modified and authorized by the Finance Manager i DMS UI

Material code will be same as of it is efined in the ERP System

-------> Material Configuration can be done using the following methods
          -----> API Intergration
          -----> Manual Creation using single


--------> Inventory Management can be configured using the attributes
          ------> category, sub - category, material code, seralized or non - seralized, available etc

